{"tid":2345564,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[對抗武肺] 究竟係咪得我一個好乖咁冇開party冇見friend","createTime":"2020-12-29T14:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T16:08:08.000Z","uid":268213,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f90f09138b1bcebf6432e533b62e90da419a0349","tid":2345564,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"每一波疫情我都只見屋企人同男朋友<br />\n（男朋友都冇見其他人）<br />\n而家開個IG都見有friend十個人咁開party<br />\n我知係聖誕節<br />\n但係咪真係有必要咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能我有睇開國際新聞<br />\n成日見英國美國啲醫生求人唔好開party同唔好見已有社交圈子以外嘅人<br />\n就算香港疫情未到咁嚴峻<br />\n我都覺得唔應該增加同我密切接觸嘅人<br />\n所以就算長假期我都冇約其他friend<br />\n<br />\n係咪得我一個咁乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時我都覺得悶同想見吓其他人㗎"},{"pid":"7b26dcc3b62c4e0fa0af920c1fdb45de175edeb8","tid":2345564,"uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2d8cfb1140107e0a4bec6c80a1de7206a8a0c1","tid":2345564,"uid":268213,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b26dcc3b62c4e0fa0af920c1fdb45de175edeb8","tid":2345564,"uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"我比較覺得我係保障緊自己同身邊嘅人"},{"pid":"f4f6bc9fdb1a62683f7176dab28fd105c9f7a734","tid":2345564,"uid":323393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:00:09.000Z","msg":"響連登問呢d把撚咩<br />\n成班毒撚話自己唔需要朋友唔需要家人<br />\n唔好話party 任何社交活動完全沒意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df92269d0cc8e32edbed2bc70c17bc8f85ffbeff","tid":2345564,"uid":321578,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"Me, 名正言順唔見外人，做舒服獨L<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hk